OL,6,FA project to transform a row of
OL,7,Fabandoned cottages into affordable
OL,8,Fhousing in Looe enters its final day
OL,9,Fof fundraising with #30,000 still to
OL,10,Fbe raised.
OL,12,FThree Seas, the organisation selling
OL,13,Fcommunity shares for the historic
OL,14,Fcoastguard flats, are confident they
OL,15,Fcan reach the #100,000 goal by
OL,16,Fmidnight on Friday, 31 May.
OL,18,FPeople in the town say the need for
OL,19,Flocal affordable housing is as
OL,20,Fdesperate as ever.
