OL,3,CLast chance to transform coastguard
OL,4,Cflats into affordable housing
OL,6,F20-year-old Kia Tonkin works six days
OL,7,Fa week in one of the town's chippies
OL,8,Fbut said finding a place to rent there
OL,9,Ffeels impossible.
OL,11,F"I need the hours anyway because I
OL,12,Fcan't find anywhere to live here," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"I live with my partner and his
OL,16,Ffamily. It's really, really nice that
OL,17,Fthey've let me live there. But I'm 20.
OL,18,FI want to start my own life."
