OL,4,Cflats into affordable housing
OL,6,FLynne Overd, a parent, said Looe is
OL,7,Funaffordable for people on local
OL,8,Fsalaries.
OL,10,FHaving living in the town for 26
OL,11,Fyears, she said: "It's very important
OL,12,Fbecause the younger families now we've
OL,13,Fgot nowhere to rent. It's very, very
OL,14,Fhard for them to find anywhere at all
OL,15,Fin Looe. So they're having to move
OL,16,Faway from their hometown."
