OL,3,CLast chance to transform coastguard
OL,4,Cflats into affordable housing
OL,6,FIt's also proving a challenge for
OL,7,Femployers like Hannah Staight, who is
OL,8,Fthe owner of Dotty's Cafe. She relies
OL,9,Fon young staff for service roles but
OL,10,Fsaid their wage needs to be
OL,11,Fcompetitive if they are travelling in
OL,12,Ffor work.
OL,14,F"It's really difficult because (they)
OL,15,Fhave to rely on trains and busses or
OL,16,Fthey're having to rely on mum and dad
OL,17,Ffor transport, which again is
OL,18,Fdifficult", Hannah said.
