OL,6,F"And then because of that we then have
OL,7,Fto think about staff wages - is it
OL,8,Fworth them travelling to us to work in
OL,9,Fcomparison to working somewhere else
OL,10,Fclose to home?"
OL,12,FThe need for housing for locals has
OL,13,Falready been recognised by Cornwall
OL,14,FCouncil when it sold the Grade II
OL,15,Flisted flats in Looe worth #640,000 to
OL,16,Fthe Three Seas Community Land Trust
OL,17,Ffor just #1.
