OL,6,FThe not-for-profit group plans to use
OL,7,Fa combination of grant funding and
OL,8,Fcommunity shares to raise enough money
OL,9,Ffor the costly repairs needed to the
OL,10,Fdilapidated interiors.
OL,12,FManager Simon Ryan said they need to
OL,13,Fclose in on #100,000 worth of
OL,14,Fcommunity shares for the project to go
OL,15,Fahead.J"It's not donation. This is
OL,16,Fshared ownership.
