OL,3,CLast chance to transform coastguard
OL,4,Cflats into affordable housing
OL,6,F"People genuinely become a part owner
OL,7,Fof this property. You put in your
OL,8,Fmoney, whether it's #100 or #25,000,
OL,9,Fand you get one vote with just past
OL,10,F100 members now. Those people are the
OL,11,Fcustodians of this housing. Long term
OL,12,Fit's them that will hold us to account
OL,13,Ffor any changes, which we are not
OL,14,Fintended to make, but it's real,
OL,15,Fgenuine democracy in practice"
