OL,6,FSimon said when they have reached
OL,7,Ftheir target and have started
OL,8,Frenovations they will be considering
OL,9,Fpeople based on a points system of how
OL,10,Fwell connected they are to the local
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,F"It's not for young people," he said.
