OL,6,F"It's for anybody who wants one of
OL,7,Fthese and can demonstrate their
OL,8,Fconnection to the town. Realistically,
OL,9,Fthere are tiny little flats, there's
OL,10,Fno parking, so probably most will go
OL,11,Fto young people leaving home for the
OL,12,Ffirst time but we're absolutely not
OL,13,Flimiting it to anybody, anybody who
OL,14,Ffits our bill."
